name: Lou Marvin Bautista
text:
kailangan daw kasi yung mindset mo is you're playing to learn. so pag natatalo ka you have to ask yourself what are you doing wrong. na hihighblood ako pag iniisip ko "ang daya ng terran/protoss" hahaha
sana kasi puwede sa sc2 pumili ng level ng kalaban. for example set mo na copper muna kalaban kahit hindi rated hehe
